OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FJersey's Environment Minister has
OL,7,Fpublished changes to his controversial
OL,8,FMarine Spatial Plan (MSP) following a
OL,9,Fconsultation into the proposals.
OL,11,FDeputy Steve Luce's plans would have
OL,12,Fseen 27% of the island's territorial
OL,13,Fwaters protected from dredging but
OL,14,Fthis figure has now been reduced to
OL,15,F23% following objections from fishers
OL,16,Fwho fear the move could decimate their
OL,17,Findustry.
