OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FThe Environment, Housing and
OL,7,FInfrastructure Scrutiny Panel has
OL,8,Flaunched a review into the planned MSP
OL,9,Fto consider whether the proposed
OL,10,Fextension of Marine Protected Areas
OL,11,F(MPAs) is fit for purpose.
OL,13,FThe Jersey MSP aims to reduce the
OL,14,Fimpact of damaging fishing activities
OL,15,Fincluding dredging and bottom trawling
OL,16,Fto protect the marine environment,
OL,17,Ffisheries and the local economy.
