OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FIt identifies the island's most
OL,7,Fsensitive marine habitats including
OL,8,Fkelp, maerl and shallow reefs in an
OL,9,Fattempt to secure their future as
OL,10,Fvital ecosystems.
OL,12,FThe Jersey MSP is part of the
OL,13,Fgovernment's plans to protect 30% of
OL,14,Fthe marine environment by 2030.
OL,16,FSome members of Jersey's fishing
OL,17,Findustry have previously told ITV News
OL,18,Fthey fear the MSP would stop them from
OL,19,Ffishing in areas they rely on to make
OL,20,Fmoney.
