OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FIn November 2023, scallop fisherman,
OL,7,FStephen Viney, said: "It's hard enough
OL,8,Fas it is and this is the final nail.
OL,9,FThe areas they're talking about are
OL,10,Fprobably the most important areas to
OL,11,Fus that we fish."
OL,13,FDon Thompson, then Chairman of the
OL,14,FJersey Fishermen's Association also
OL,15,Faccused the island's government of
OL,16,Frushing plans without considering
OL,17,Ffishers' livelihoods.
