OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FJersey's government started
OL,7,Fconsultation into the original plans
OL,8,Fin October 2023 and adjustments have
OL,9,Fnow been made.
OL,11,FDeputy Luce said: "I am grateful to
OL,12,Feveryone who took the time to give
OL,13,Ftheir views on the plan during the
OL,14,Fconsultation period.
OL,16,F"We received over 150 comments which
OL,17,Fhas all been taken into consideration
OL,18,Fwhen publishing this draft."
