OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FHe added: "I'd like to think that
OL,7,Fthere is something positive for
OL,8,Feveryone in this revised plan and
OL,9,Fespecially for those who responded to
OL,10,Fthe consultation.
OL,12,F"The plan helps us understand how
OL,13,Fpeople value and interact with our
OL,14,Fmarine environment. It's important we
OL,15,Ffind a balance between the different
OL,16,Fuses we have for our marine
OL,17,Fenvironment and to make sure we
OL,18,Finteract with our local ecosystems in
OL,19,Fa sustainable manner."
