OL,3,CProposed protections on Jersey waters
OL,4,Creduced amid fears for fishing
OL,6,FDeputy Luce said he was "looking
OL,7,Fforward" to debating the plans later
OL,8,Fin the year.
OL,10,FThe MSP will be reviewed by the
OL,11,FEnvironment, Housing and
OL,12,FInfrastructure Scrutiny Panel ahead of
OL,13,Fa States' debate during autumn 2024.
OL,15,FDeputy Hilary Jeune, Chair of the
OL,16,FScrutiny Panel, said: "While the aims
OL,17,Fof the MSP, to protect our marine
OL,18,Fenvironment for future generations,
OL,19,Fare laudable, we have to ensure the
OL,20,Fplan, as it is being proposed, is the
OL,21,Fright one for our island."
